<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.18">
<l>maṇṇum malaiyuṅ  kaṭalu mulakēḻu</l>
<l>muṇṇun tiṟantu makiḻntuṇṇum piḷḷaikku</l>
<l>vaṇṇa meḻilkoḷ makarak kuḻaiyivai</l>
<l>tiṇṇa miruntavā kāṇīrē cēyiḻai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with red jewels, see the quality of the sturdiness</l>
<l>of these Makara earrings, beautiful in colour,</l>
<l>of the child who, while joyfully eating, revealed that [he] had eaten</l>
<l>the lands, the mountains, the oceans, and the seven worlds. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
